            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://kotaku.com/big-4k-blu-ray-uhd-collection-sale-box-sets-discount-1851742303<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><figure id="" data-id="2f4a5ab04c34f46999e27835982bbd11" data-recommend-id="image://2f4a5ab04c34f46999e27835982bbd11" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false" contenteditable="false" draggable="false"><div contenteditable="false" data-link-reference="" data-link-target="" data-syndicationrights="true" data-imagerights="fair-use" data-hide="false" data-hidecredit="false"><p><figcaption>Image<!-- -->: <!-- -->Gruv / Kotaku</figcaption></p></div><span data-id="2f4a5ab04c34f46999e27835982bbd11" data-recommend-id="image://2f4a5ab04c34f46999e27835982bbd11" data-format="jpg" data-width="1920" data-height="1080" data-lightbox="true" data-recommended="false" data-hide="false"></span></figure><div><p>A big <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/amazon-4k-uhd-bluray-batman-dune-barbie-joker-godzilla-1851734723&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/amazon-4k-uhd-bluray-batman-dune-barbie-joker-godzilla-1851734723">4K Blu-ray movie collection</a></span> sale is happening right now, letting you grab all of the movies in some popular franchises—like <em>Harry Potter</em> and <em>Mad Max</em>—for around the cost of a <em>single</em>, new UHD film. But you’d better act fast as this deal ends in a few days! </p><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><div data-video-id="197298" data-monetizable="true" data-position="sidebar" data-video-title="Live Forever in the Universe of 'New World: Aeternum'" data-video-blog-id="9" data-video-network="kotaku" data-video-duration="108" data-playlist="197298,197284,197260" data-current="197298"><div><p>Live Forever in the Universe of 'New World: Aeternum'</p></div><video disablepictureinpicture="" muted="" playsinline="" width="100%" height="100%" crossorigin="anonymous" preload="none"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197298/197298_240p.mp4" label="240p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197298/197298_480p.mp4" label="480p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197298/197298_720p.mp4" label="720p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/197298/197298_1080p.mp4" label="1080p" type="video/mp4"></video></div><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><p><span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://go.skimresources.com?id=33330X1579802&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=IV-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gruv.com%2Fcategory%2F4k_uhd_deals&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=33330X1579802&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=IV-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gruv.com%2Fcategory%2F4k_uhd_deals" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim" data-vtas-click="self:InlineUrl:inline-url-postbody">Gruv.com is currently doing a large, 4K UHD  sale</a></span> on a selection of movie collections. So instead of just <em>Jurassic World</em> or one <em>Fast &amp; Furious</em> movie, these collections often contain the entire franchise, or most of it. For example, you can buy the<em> </em><span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://go.skimresources.com?id=33330X1579802&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=IV-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gruv.com%2Fproduct%2Frocky_6_film_collection_4k_ultra_hd_uhd&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=33330X1579802&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=IV-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gruv.com%2Fproduct%2Frocky_6_film_collection_4k_ultra_hd_uhd" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim" data-vtas-click="self:InlineUrl:inline-url-postbody"><em>Rocky Ultimate Knockout Collection</em></a></span>, which contains all six <em>Rocky</em> films, for just $70 instead of the usual $100 price tag. These collections are a great way to build up your <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;Internal link&quot;,&quot;https://kotaku.com/best-buy-dvd-blu-ray-games-sales-stop-2024-1851136668?_gl=1*ecb6pn*_ga*MTM0Mjk0ODIxMC4xNjkxNzY3NjQ2*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNzEzNjYyOS4xMDEuMS4xNzM3MTM4MDg3LjYwLjAuMA..&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://kotaku.com/best-buy-dvd-blu-ray-games-sales-stop-2024-1851136668?_gl=1*ecb6pn*_ga*MTM0Mjk0ODIxMC4xNjkxNzY3NjQ2*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNzEzNjYyOS4xMDEuMS4xNzM3MTM4MDg3LjYwLjAuMA..">physical movie collection</a></span>, especially when they are on sale like this. (And for those wondering: Amazon seems to be price-matching some of these deals, <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://x.com/Wario64/status/1880285933339308507&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://x.com/Wario64/status/1880285933339308507" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">like the <em>Matrix </em>collection</a></span>, but not <em>all </em>of them.)</p><p><span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://go.skimresources.com?id=33330X1579802&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=IV-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gruv.com%2Fcategory%2F4k_uhd_deals&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=33330X1579802&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=IV-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gruv.com%2Fcategory%2F4k_uhd_deals" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim" data-vtas-click="self:InlineUrl:inline-url-postbody">Gruv’s 4K UHD collection sale</a></span> ends on January 20, so don’t wait too long if you want to grab any of these discounted box sets. </p><p>Just remember you’ll need a UHD Blu-ray player to watch these movies. (Your PS5 and Xbox Series X are solid UHD players, assuming they have disc slots!) And you’ll need to make sure your TV is 4K compatible.  </p><p>Here are some of the best movie collections currently on sale:</p><ul data-type="List" data-style="Bullet"><li><strong>James Bond: The Daniel Craig 5-Film Collection</strong> - $40 ($90)</li><li><strong> Stanley Kubrick: 3-Film Collection</strong> - $27 ($80) </li><li><strong>Harry Potter: Complete 8-Film Collection</strong> - $70 ($90) </li><li><strong>The Matrix: 4-Film Collection</strong> - $35 ($85) </li><li><strong>Jurassic World Complete Collection</strong> - $45 ($100) </li><li><strong>The Mummy Trilogy</strong> - $25 ($60) </li><li><strong>Mad Max 5-Film Collection </strong>- $65 ($110) </li></ul><ul data-type="List" data-style="Bullet"><li><strong>Fast &amp; Furious 10-Movie Collection</strong> - $70 ($140) </li><li><strong>Back to the Future: The Ultimate Trilogy Collection </strong>- $31 ($60)</li></ul></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
